- Auth: NextAuth (email/password or OAuth)
- Payments: Stripe
- Storage: Uploadcare or Cloudinary for product images
- Deployment: Vercel for app, Neon or Supabase for Postgres, Stripe for payments

Project setup
1) Create the app
- npx create-next-app@latest shop
- cd shop
- npm i @prisma/client prisma next-auth @auth/prisma-adapter zod bcrypt stripe @stripe/stripe-js react-hook-form uploadcare-widget
- npm i -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer @types/bcrypt @types/node typescript

2) Tailwind config
